The goal is to prove that `∀ (m : ℂ) (x_1 : H), ComplexMeasure.integral (@cfc_toComplexMeasure H inst✝² inst✝¹ inst✝ a ha x (m • x_1)) f = (RingHom.id ℂ) m • ComplexMeasure.integral (@cfc_toComplexMeasure H inst✝² inst✝¹ inst✝ a ha x x_1) f`.

This is the linearity of the integral. Let's complete the proof.

